name: Assent Protocol
public_notice: The smart-contract protocol/ owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Assent Protocol is a DAO ecosystem that aims to become the #1 multi chain DeFi bank for both investors and projects alike. Assent Protocol will do so in a way no other project has done before. By solving the main DeFi 1.0 and DeFi 2.0 problems, Assent Protocol is introducing DeFi 2.5.
